<font color="yellow">Benarkah?</font>

520
00:49:07,412 --> 00:49:09,222
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih.</font>

521
00:49:13,012 --> 00:49:14,822
<font color="yellow">Biar kubelikan minum.</font>

522
00:49:20,012 --> 00:49:25,912
<font color="yellow">Seo Woo Oppa menyantap
makanan yang kubuat untuknya!</font>

523
00:49:25,912 --> 00:49:27,822
<font color="yellow">Ya ampun!</font>

524
00:49:40,512 --> 00:49:42,182
<font color="yellow"><i>[Kecocokan dengan Kang Seo Woo:
95 persen]</i></font>

525
00:49:42,912 --> 00:49:48,912
<font color="yellow">Apa? Tidak mungkin!
Kami berjodoh?</font>

526
00:49:48,912 --> 00:49:50,722
<font color="yellow">95 persen?</font>

527
00:49:53,222 --> 00:49:54,322
<font color="yellow">Sedang apa kau?</font>

528
00:49:54,322 --> 00:49:58,322
<font color="yellow">Oh, tidak kenapa-kenapa.
